video.title: The Thundermans
video.synopsis: A twin sister strives to be a superhero as her brother aspires to be a supervillain, but they and their family must keep their superpowers secret.

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe and Max babysit Nora and Billy while their parents enjoy an evening out, but they break a big rule and now have to deal with the consequences.
episodes.title: Adventures in Supersitting

episodes.synopsis: Max plots to sabotage a dinner party attended by Phoebe's crush but must join forces with his sister when an unexpected guest also shows up.
episodes.title: Dinner Party

episodes.synopsis: Max alters his grades to get into Phoebe's advanced class and compete against her in a Math Bowl. Hank, Nora and Billy try to catch a newspaper thief.
episodes.title: Report Card

episodes.synopsis: A prank war between Phoebe and Max escalates. Hank and Barb try a new approach to parenting in an effort to get the younger kids to do their chores.
episodes.title: Phoebe vs. Max

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe and Max completely take over Billy and Nora's school projects in an effort to beat each other at the kids' upcoming school science fair.
episodes.title: Weird Science Fair

episodes.synopsis: With their parents away at the reading of a rich uncle's will, Phoebe house-sits a Venus flytrap from school that Max desperately wants to steal.
episodes.title: Weekend Guest

episodes.synopsis: When they use their superpowers on Ditch Day, Phoebe and Max remember that their school has security cameras and must try to erase the footage.
episodes.title: Ditch Day

episodes.synopsis: To help an overcommitted Phoebe, Max clones his sister so she can be in two places at once, but the clone creates more problems than it solves.
episodes.title: Phoebe's a Clone Now

episodes.synopsis: To earn money to buy new cell phones, Phoebe and Max get part-time jobs at Wong's Pizza Palace but they're soon in over their heads on a huge order.
episodes.title: This Looks Like a Job For

episodes.synopsis: The family's superpowers malfunction thanks to a passing comet, forcing Phoebe and Max to reluctantly help each other keep the problems under control.
episodes.title: Going Wonkers

episodes.synopsis: When the kids damage a new car that Hank bought for Barb as an anniversary present, they're forced to turn to their superhero cousin for help.
episodes.title: Restaurant Crashers

episodes.synopsis: A neighborhood watch is formed to catch a mysterious vandal and Phoebe suspects Max -- until she discovers her brother is hiding a different secret.
episodes.title: Crime After Crime

episodes.synopsis: Max is inadvertently elected class president instead of Phoebe, who becomes his vice president and starts to resent him stealing her good ideas.
episodes.title: You Stole My Thunder, Man

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe develops the superpower of "Thundersense" -- sensing danger before it happens -- and uses her newfound ability to impress her classmates.
episodes.title: Thundersense

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe and Max host a cool birthday party with their friends at the Pizza Palace instead of their usual family shindig, but Mrs. Wong ends up frozen.
episodes.title: Have an Ice Birthday

episodes.synopsis: In order to win a dream vacation, the Thundermans enter a competition but, unable to agree on the destination, they enter as two different teams.
episodes.title: Up, Up, and Vacay!

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe uses telekinesis to save her first sleepover and is punished by having to wear an ankle bracelet that prevents her use of superpowers.
episodes.title: Nothing to Lose Sleepover

episodes.synopsis: The twins team up to take down mean girl Veronica, who sabotaged Phoebe in the choir and manipulated Max into doing her homework for her.
episodes.title: Pretty Little Choirs

episodes.synopsis: The twins take Billy to the hospital with an injury and Max faints at the sight of a needle, so the others must stop doctors from scanning his brain.
episodes.title: Paging Dr. Thunderman

episodes.synopsis: Hank is the new science teacher at Phoebe and Max's school but when he eats turkey sandwiches that make him sleepy, they use their powers to help him.
episodes.title: Breaking Dad

episodes.synopsis: After Phoebe meets up with her crush and his baby brother in the park, Max and the younger kids accidentally take the child home with them.
episodes.title: Four Supes and a Baby

episodes.synopsis: Everyone thinks Max cheated to win a month of free pizza. Phoebe and Cherry's friendship is tested when only one of them makes the cheerleading squad.
episodes.title: Cheer and Present Danger

episodes.synopsis: Hank brings the Thunder Van back from Metroburg so a reluctant Phoebe can train as a superhero, but the kids sneak the vehicle out for a joyride.
episodes.title: Thunder Van

episodes.synopsis: When Billy steals a vase from a museum for Phoebe to present as her own at an art auction, the kids must return it before anyone realizes it's gone.
episodes.title: Change of Art

episodes.synopsis: Max loses his status as the school's bad boy when a group of freshmen he recruits to be his followers turns the tables on him with a humiliating prank.
episodes.title: Max’s Minions

episodes.synopsis: When they use one of Max's inventions to make Hank and Barb act like teenagers, Phoebe and Max quickly regret it since they must now be the parents.
episodes.title: Parents Just Don’t Thunderstand

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe is devastated when she believes that her concert tickets were shredded but it's actually Max who has stolen them to take his crush to the show.
episodes.title: Shred It Go

episodes.synopsis: Max's new bandmate, Oyster, is a bad boy who Phoebe tries to entice by becoming a bad girl, until she realizes he's more in love with his guitar.
episodes.title: Pheebs Will Rock You

episodes.synopsis: A trip to the mall to buy a watch as a birthday present for Hank devolves into a fight and an encounter with security for Phoebe and Max.
episodes.title: Mall Time Crooks

episodes.synopsis: Max resorts to desperate measures in his effort to get some footage for a contest-winning "epic fail" video of Phoebe practicing her ballet dancing.
episodes.title: You’ve Got Fail

episodes.synopsis: When their friends start hanging out with each other, a panicked Phoebe and Max try to undermine the new relationships with a bad trip to the movies.
episodes.title: The Neverfriending Story

episodes.synopsis: The Thundermans team up with the Hathaways and the Prestons in New Orleans to stop a supervillain that has escaped from Ghost World on Halloween.
episodes.title: Haunted Thundermans

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe and Max accidentally sell Barb's old Electress utility belt to a fan at a family garage sale and must get it back before their mom finds out.
episodes.title: Who’s Your Mommy?

episodes.synopsis: Max turns Billy into a rat in order to win a race against his bandmates, but Billy gets a taste for the acclaim and doesn't want to be human again.
episodes.title: The Amazing Rat Race

episodes.synopsis: Max is having a Scroogelike Christmas until the ghosts of Christmas Past, Present and Future appear to show him what the holiday spirit is all about.
episodes.title: Winter Thunderland

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe starts secretly dating the son of a retired supervillain that just moved to Hiddenville and who happens to be Thunder Man's longtime archenemy.
episodes.title: Meet the Evilmans

episodes.synopsis: Max launches an investigation to try to find out who is responsible for turning his skin blue in the middle of a date with Maddy at Splatburger.
episodes.title: Blue Detective

episodes.synopsis: The Thundermans prepare for an exciting new addition to the family while Max accompanies Dr. Colosso to receive the Villain of the Decade Award.
episodes.title: A Hero Is Born Pt. I

episodes.synopsis: When his fellow villains want to deny Dr. Colosso his award due to inactivity during his time as a rabbit, he betrays Max, who must be rescued.
episodes.title: A Hero Is Born Pt. II

episodes.synopsis: Max develops a taste for a life of luxury when he uses his powers to help Phoebe in a tennis tournament at the country club Link's family attends.
episodes.title: Doubles Trouble

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe plots to make the quarreling Max and Link become friends, but her scheme works too well and soon Link is spending more time with Max than her.
episodes.title: It’s Not What You Link

episodes.synopsis: After she sneaks out to a party and saves someone's life there, Phoebe asks Max to take all the credit, which suddenly turns him into a big hero.
episodes.title: Cape Fear

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe discovers that Max is behind the mysterious pranks occurring at school, but faces some tough consequences by refusing to give him up.
episodes.title: Call of Lunch Duty

episodes.synopsis: Max uses personal information about Phoebe and Link in a song and causes problems in their relationship. Hank and Barb teach Billy and Nora a lesson.
episodes.title: One Hit Thunder

episodes.synopsis: Phoebe is excited to team up with the school's cool kids on a project, only to discover they're not all that interested in doing the work.
episodes.title: The Girl with the Dragon Snafu
